aacute;tor, kempingcikk, vitorla, ejt?erny?, napellenz?, aut&oacute;takar&oacute;, b&uacute;tortakar&oacute; stb.&nbsp;<br />- z&aacute;szl&oacute;, vas&uacute;ti &eacute;s haj&oacute; jelz?z&aacute;szl&oacute; stb.<br />- porrongy, konyharuha &eacute;s hasonl&oacute; cikk, ment?mell&eacute;ny, ejt?erny? stb.&nbsp;<br />- az elektromos meleg&iacute;t?vel felszerelt takar&oacute; textilr&eacute;szeinek elk&uuml;l&ouml;n&uuml;lt gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa<br />- a k&eacute;zi sz&ouml;v&eacute;s? falk&aacute;rpit (gobelin) gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa<br /><br />Nem ebbe a szak&aacute;gazatba tartozik:&nbsp;<br />- a m?szaki rendeltet&eacute;s? konfekcion&aacute;lt textil&aacute;ru gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>K&ouml;t&eacute;l&aacute;ru gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa</h1>\r\n<p>Ebbe a szak&aacute;gazatba tartozik:<br />- a zsineg, a k&ouml;t&eacute;l&aacute;ru &eacute;s a k&aacute;bel gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa textilsz&aacute;lb&oacute;l, szalagb&oacute;l vagy hasonl&oacute; anyagb&oacute;l, az impregn&aacute;lt, bevont, bor&iacute;tott, gumival vagy m?anyaggal burkolt is<br />- a zsinegb?l, k&ouml;t&eacute;l&aacute;rub&oacute;l, illetve k&ouml;t&eacute;lb?l csom&oacute;zott h&aacute;l&oacute;k gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa<br />- a k&ouml;t&eacute;lb?l, h&aacute;l&oacute;b&oacute;l k&eacute;sz&iacute;tett term&eacute;kek gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa: pl. hal&aacute;szh&aacute;l&oacute;, haj&oacute;k &uuml;tk&ouml;z? p&aacute;rn&aacute;ja, vontat&oacute;k&ouml;t&eacute;l, heveder, f&eacute;mgy?r?kkel ell&aacute;tott k&ouml;t&eacute;l stb.<br /><br />Nem ebbe a szak&aacute;gazatba tartozik:<br />- a hajh&aacute;l&oacute;k gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa,&nbsp;<br />- a dr&oacute;tk&ouml;t&eacute;l gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa,&nbsp;<br />- a mer&iacute;t?h&aacute;l&oacute; gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa sporthorg&aacute;szathoz,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1>K&ouml;t&ouml;tt, hurkolt kelme gy&aacute;rt&aacute;sa</h1>\r\n<p>Ebbe a szak&aacute;gazatba tartozik:<br />- a k&ouml;t&ouml;tt vagy hurkolt kelm&eacute;k gy&aacute;rt&a